      <title>以色列关于谁应该被要求参军的争论</title>
      <link>https://npr.org/2024/04/17/1196980542/the-debate-in-israel-over-who-should-be-required-serve-in-the-military</link>
      <description><![CDATA[极端正统的以色列人长期以来一直被免除义务兵役。但哈马斯 10 月 7 日的袭击以及以色列随后的军事反应引发了变革的呼声。政府关于是否终止豁免的决定会产生重大政治后果。]]></description>
      <guid>https://npr.org/2024/04/17/1196980542/the-debate-in-israel-over-who-should-be-required-serve-in-the-military</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 17 Apr 2024 18:12:16 GMT</pubDate>
